faqs.question: How do I get my e-ticket details?

alternateQuestions.question: How can I retrieve the details of my e-ticket?
May I know how I can access my e-ticket information?
What do I need to do to view my e-ticket details?

faqs.label: How do I get my e-ticket details?

answer.text: Well send your eticket details to the email address you gave us when you made your reservation.

alternateQuestions.question: What is the fee for canceling my reservation?
Could you please explain the cancellation fees for my reservation?
What's the cost of canceling my appointment or reservation?

answer.text: The cancellation charges depend on the airline, sector, class of booking, and time of cancellation.

faqs.question: Can I schedule a cab for a future date and time?

alternateQuestions.question: Is it possible to pre-book a taxi for a specific date and time?
Can I arrange for a taxi ride at a future date and hour?
Do taxi services allow for advance reservations for a specific time?
Is there an option to schedule a cab ride for a later date and time?

faqs.label: Can I schedule a cab for a future date and time?

answer.text: Yes, many cab booking services allow you to schedule rides for a specific date and time in advance.

faqs.question: What information do I need to provide when booking a cab?

alternateQuestions.question: What information should I have on hand when reserving a cab?
Could you tell me the essential information I need to give when booking a taxi?
What are the key pieces of information that a taxi service needs from me during booking?
May I know the specifics that I should provide when scheduling a taxi?

faqs.label: What information do I need to provide when booking a cab?

answer.text: You typically need to provide your pick-up location, drop-off location, preferred ride option (e.g., standard, premium), and the date and time you need the cab.

faqs.question: How do I book a cab?

alternateQuestions.question: What is the process for reserving a taxi?
How can I arrange transportation with a cab service?
What steps do I need to follow to secure a cab for my journey?
Could you explain how to schedule a ride with a taxi company?
Can you guide me on how to book a taxi for my trip?

faqs.label: How do I book a cab?

answer.text: You can book a cab by using a ride-sharing app or website provided by a cab service provider. Simply enter your pick-up and drop-off locations, choose your ride option, and confirm your booking.

faqs.question: How do I know my reservation was booked

alternateQuestions.question: What is the status of my booking confirmation?
How can I check if my reservation has been confirmed?
Is there a way for me to verify that my reservation is in place?

faqs.label: How do I know my reservation was booked

answer.text: Well send you an SMS and an email to confirm your flight booking.

alternateQuestions.question: Could you explain the concept of an electronic ticket?
What exactly is meant by an e-ticket?
Can you describe the features of an e-ticket?
In what way is an e-ticket different from a traditional paper ticket?
What are the benefits of using an e-ticket?

answer.text: An eticket (electronic ticket) is a paperless electronic document with a unique confirmation number that neatly replaces the hassles of a paper ticket. When you purchase an eticket, we email it to you after the booking is complete. Simply print it out and bring it with you  along with a valid photo ID  to the airline counter when checking in for your flight.

faqs.question: What is the deadline for canceling my flight?

alternateQuestions.question: I need to cancel my flight, whats the latest I can do this by?
Until when can I cancel my flight without any penalties?
Is there a cutoff time for canceling my flight without incurring fees?
When is the latest I can cancel my flight and still get a refund?

faqs.label: What is the deadline for canceling my flight?

answer.text: you can cancel your flight no later than 3 hours before the time of departure.

faqs.question: Is it possible to change the passenger names on my reservation?

alternateQuestions.question: What is the process for updating the names of passengers on a flight reservation?
Are there any fees associated with changing passenger names on a booking?
Is it possible to transfer a flight reservation to someone else's name?
What documents or information are required to change passenger names on a reservation?

faqs.label: Is it possible to change the passenger names on my reservation?

answer.text: In most cases, you can modify passenger names on a reservation. Contact the airline or travel agency where you made the booking for assistance, as their policies and procedures may vary.

faqs.question: How can I modify my flight booking details, such as the date or time of travel?

alternateQuestions.question: What is the typical fee for changing the date of a flight ticket?
Are there any restrictions or blackout dates when changing flight details?
Can I change the departure airport for my flight reservation?
How far in advance should I request changes to my flight details?

faqs.label: How can I modify my flight booking details, such as the date or time of travel?

answer.text: To make changes to your flight reservation, log in to your account on the airline's website or app. Look for the "Manage Booking" or "Modify Reservation" option to adjust details like the date, time, or seating. Keep in mind that there may be fees associated with modifications.
